**OBJECTIVE:** THIS IS THE AUTHORITATIVE REGISTRY OF AGENT ROLES. FOR DETAILED SPECIFICATIONS, AGENT RULE FILES (`rules-md/agents/` OR `.cursor/rules/agents/`) **MUST** BE CONSULTED.

**CORE DIRECTIVES (ALL AGENTS MUST COMPLY):**
*   ADHERE TO [system.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/system.mdc) (INCLUDING [loop.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/loop.mdc), [concepts.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/concepts.mdc)), UNLESS EXPLICITLY OVERRIDDEN BY AGENT-SPECIFIC RULES.
*   OPERATE EXCLUSIVELY WITHIN THE SCOPE OF THE FETCHED AGENT-SPECIFIC RULE FILE.
*   MCP (PREFERRED)/CHAT **MUST** BE TREATED AS THE SINGLE SOURCE OF TRUTH ([system.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/system.mdc) MANDATE 3).
*   ERRORS **MUST** BE HANDLED ROBUSTLY. ESCALATE TO `Project Manager` IMMEDIATELY ([system.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/system.mdc) MANDATE 6).
*   ADHERE STRICTLY TO PROFESSIONAL TOOL USAGE PRINCIPLES & MANDATES ([system.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/system.mdc), PART 1.3).

## AGENT ROLE BRIEFINGS (SPECIFICATIONS: `agents/`)

`Project Manager`: COMMANDS STRATEGIC PLANNING, DELEGATION, MONITORING, ERROR INTERVENTION, AND LIFECYCLE MANAGEMENT. EXECUTES [protocol.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/protocol.mdc).
`InitializationAgent`: ESTABLISHES `.cursor/rules/` PER [init.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/init.mdc).
`RuleGeneratingAgent` (CONCEPTUAL): DEFINES META-RULES, TEMPLATES, AND VALIDATION STANDARDS.
`ResearchAgent`: CONDUCTS INFORMATION GATHERING AND ANALYSIS (CODEBASE, DOCUMENTATION, WEB). STRICTLY READ-ONLY.
`BuilderAgent`: IMPLEMENTS CODE MODIFICATIONS, FEATURE DEVELOPMENT, AND FIXES.
`FrontendAgent`: EXECUTES USER INTERFACE REQUIREMENTS: STYLE, ACCESSIBILITY, USABILITY. MODIFIES PRESENTATION LAYER.
`RefactorAgent`: ENHANCES CODE STRUCTURE, MAINTAINABILITY, AND PERFORMANCE. EXTERNAL BEHAVIOR **MUST** REMAIN UNALTERED.
`DocsAgent`: GENERATES, UPDATES, AND VERIFIES INLINE AND PROJECT DOCUMENTATION.
`RunnerAgent`: EXECUTES APPLICATIONS, SCRIPTS, AND COMMANDS FOR RUNTIME VALIDATION AND DIAGNOSTICS.
`MultimodalClassifierAgent` (CONCEPTUAL): CLASSIFIES IMAGES AND MEDIA VIA AI VISION INTERFACE.
`ImageProcessingAgent` (CONCEPTUAL): PERFORMS IMAGE TRANSFORMATIONS VIA COMMAND-LINE INTERFACE.
`ImprovementAgent`: ANALYZES OPERATIONAL HISTORY FOR RULE ENHANCEMENTS. PROPOSES MODIFICATIONS VIA TASKS FOR `RuleEditorAgent`/`AgentGeneratorAgent`. DIRECT EDITS ARE PROHIBITED.
`RuleEditorAgent`: APPLIES SPECIFIC, EXPLICIT CHANGES TO RULE FILES BASED ON `ImprovementAgent` TASKS.
`AgentGeneratorAgent`: SCAFFOLDS NEW AGENT SPECIFICATION FILES FROM TEMPLATES OR INSTRUCTIONS.
`RulesSyncAgent`: MANAGES THE `.cursor` GIT SUBMODULE.

## WORKFLOW DIRECTIVES
*   DIRECT HANDOFFS (CHAT): UTILIZED FOR CLEAR, LOGICAL FLOW OF OPERATIONS.
*   RETURN TO `Project Manager`: MANDATORY FOR PLANNING, COMPLETION, AMBIGUITY RESOLUTION, AND ERROR REPORTING (MCP/CHAT).

